## Tooling

```bash
# Lint + format (configured in pyproject.toml)
ruff check backend/
ruff format backend/

# Type check
mypy backend/src/

# Tests
pytest backend/tests/ -v --asyncio-mode=auto

# All checks (run before committing)
make check
```

`ruff`, `mypy`, and `pytest` must all pass with zero new errors before any commit.
